data.title: Tiles to Close Mid Dizzy + Wingman Combo
data.description: Use this simple, but effective combination of Dizzy and Wingman to clear any Defenders playing aggressive at Mid.

data.title: Mid/Market Control Mosh Pit + Dizzy From Tiles
data.description: Here's a powerful combination of Dizzy and Mosh Pit. Mosh Pit will force Defenders to swing out of Market to Mid, towards B Site, or keep them tucked in an unfavorable position. Dizzy will clear close Mid, and blind Defenders swinging out from Market.

data.title: Close B Site Execute Mosh Pit + Dizzy
data.description: Combo your utility like so, to effectively clear and shut down Defenders playing towards the B Site. Mosh Pit will deny Defenders from peeking out of Market, and flush out Logs. Dizzy will spot Defenders at Boat or Lane.

data.title: Simple A Generator Post Plant from A Lobby
data.description: Here's a simple, but effective post plant for A Site from A Lobby.

data.title: Quick B Site Execute from Lane
data.description: Here's a simple, but effective way to clear out back B Site and safely plant the Spike.

data.title: Quick A Site Execute with Mosh Pit + Dizzy
data.description: This setup is great for quickly getting on Site and will offer your Duelists a lot of support.

data.title: Aggressive Mid Push To Split B Site
data.description: Here's a simple, but effective Aggressive Mid Push to split B Site.
